name: Zombie Queen 1.1
description:
There's no doubt here that she is long gone. However... That doesn't mean that she is not here anymore. 
What can be better than a ghost zombie girl to celebrate the beginning of October 2021? HD version of the artwork "Queen of Decay 8bit (BW)" (2021)

Token exclusively distributed to holders of "Queen of Decay 8bit (BW)", not available for primary sale.
